Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.94,sign_0_1_Episode_28,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3211)}Episode 28
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.94,sign_0_2_Only_Diamond_Can,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3211)}Only a Diamond Can \NPolish a Diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:08.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I only have memories of part of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:12.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I didn't lose \Nmy memories from trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:18.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,My very life has only existed\N since that day eight years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Everything before that is darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:31.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere in that darkness, \NI floated aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:41.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's hand broke through \Nthe bounds of that void
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:44.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,and dragged me into the outer world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:54.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,That hand was yours, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:59.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:03.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I followed this case to find that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:07.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:09.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I will, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:13.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,You're worthy of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't he defend himself with gravity?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike a bullet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:27.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,the subspace I control doesn't \Nabide by the laws of physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:33.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,The subspace is a separate world, \Nclosed off from regular space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:52.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot come in unless I invite you.\N Nor can you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:55.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You've left me outside while \Ndeploying your subspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You must know what my ability is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:01:59.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:03.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that didn't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:05.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I should have expected as \Nmuch from Arahabaki's incarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:17.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya-kun. You can't touch me in this space,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:20.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,but I can attack you as I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:45.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Any ability that touches \Nthat dolt gets nullified.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:48.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to quarantine \Nhim with your subspace,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:51.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,you'll make a good trench for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:53.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,True, his existence is heretical.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:58.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate anti-gifted, \Nwith no peer even in the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The west?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:23.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You look well for someone \Nwho's been dead, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, former boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:32.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he could have hurt \Nthat idiot with his special ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:40.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The former boss's giant scythe\N isn't an ability. It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:44.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,So it could kill you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:48.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,The former boss is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do, Randou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:57.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,My ability can turn corpses\N stored in my subspace
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:01.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,into supernatural beings I command.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:05.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I can only control one at a time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:08.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:13.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You've been hiding that ability from \Nthe organization this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:21.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I was formerly a gifted western spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I came to this nation to obtain\N a high-energy being
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:29.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,the government of Japan \Nhad supposedly discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:32.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,And that's Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:37.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,My sole purpose for this \Nplan has been to kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:42.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya-kun, and subsume you as the replacement
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,supernatural being for the former boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:51.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-kun, if the boss were \Nto learn what you just have,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,he would attempt to have me assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:58.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I regretfully ask you to die\N with Chuuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.52,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:07.96,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,There's no danger involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:21.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:23.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:27.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to like working for the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:32.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,In the outside world, \Ndeath is pushed away from everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:38.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But in the Mafia's world, death is an \Nextension of and a part of everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:41.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to think that's more accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:45.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,After all, to die isn't the opposite of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:49.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's merely a component \Nof the process of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Without observing death up close,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:55.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,one can't capture the full picture \Nof what it means to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:06:00.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, \Nthe suicidal maniac wants to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:01.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to think it's worth trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:08.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,It's death time for kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:13.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:44.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Eight years ago, I tried to take you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:47.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Arahabaki, as my supernatural being.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:54.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,But the moment Arahabaki emerged, \Nit decimated the surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:58.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make the same mistake twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:03.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll end your life\N thoroughly and subsume you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:29.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,You soaked up the impact by increasing \Nyour gravity and density?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:36.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to tell you why I was keeping \Nboth my hands tucked away until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if I ever felt like I was about to lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:45.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,that feeling might give me\N a reason to be fond...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:51.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,...of my humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:56.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Once I subsume you, perhaps\Nthe coldness I feel will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Chuuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:06.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} move, Dazai, you piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:20.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:30.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:48.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot escape gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:09:01.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If Randou-san's subspace vanishes, \Nnaturally, so will you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:13.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Let me thank you for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:40.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, shitty Dazai? A magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:45.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Chuuya, do you really think \NI'd be wearing a cast for no reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:49.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to tell us everything, \Naren't you, Randou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,That day, eight years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:59.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,my spy partner and I infiltrated this nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:04.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We were here to take the high-energy being
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:08.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,the military was supposedly \Nhiding in a secret facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:12.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But the moment I took the being,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:16.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,my partner betrayed me and our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:21.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He and I fought over the being and, in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:25.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,we were discovered and confronted \Nby the Japanese military.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:32.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,In order to escape, I unleashed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:38.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,the being I'd stolen,\N and tried to take control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:43.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,In that instant you blew up the \Nfacility along with all its records,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and I lost my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,My name isn't Randou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:02.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Someone of this nation simply \Nmisread the hat that I wore,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and gave the name to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:09.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I killed him with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:16.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect you aren't Arahabaki itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:21.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,but a human being chosen as a vessel \Nto keep Arahabaki under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:28.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,But you are strong, not as\N the Aragami but as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:30.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever may live inside you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,you are already you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:39.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:47.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,All people, all creatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:51.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,live without knowing what \Nthey really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:57.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:03.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Randou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the least bit cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:33.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the ass, even in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:40.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,The Port Mafia took all the records \Nyou'd collected on Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:43.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I have no leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:50.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that you would have told anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,about that stuff, even if you'd been alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:56.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you, Chuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:10.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:12.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,We did some soul-searching \Nafter what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,We have a good understanding \Nof the Sheep's problems now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:27.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,So we all talked it over \Nand came up with a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:31.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,If it's something you decided\N together, I won't—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:41.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,We attack you from outside your periphery,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,when your guard is completely down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you won't have \Ntime to use gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Chuuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:54.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,You should try not to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:57.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,I rubbed rat poison on the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:01.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,Your limbs will be numb \Nand immobilized for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:07.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have had to go through \Nthis if you weren't so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,This is the solution we chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:18.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,We'll team up with the GSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,We all came to the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:25.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,that if you were to side with the Port Mafia,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:27.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,you'd get everyone in the Sheep killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I would never betray the organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, the GSS doesn't \Nchange its loyalties on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:38.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,They can be trusted \Nas long as they can profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:43.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,This is the smarter way to fight\N against the Port Mafia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:50.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I was the fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,Get him! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:09.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,He may be weakened by the poison, \Nbut it won't be enough to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:10.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,Find him quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Shirase,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him live!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,"Leader," my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:28.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one ruining the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:30.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chuuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're in a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here, shitty Dazai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to kill me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:42.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from Mori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:46.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He wants me to officially \Nrecruit you into the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to make me\N owe you by saving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The message isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:54.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just here for a massacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-san is a pretty demanding employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:16:02.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I joined the Port Mafia, \Nhe put me in charge of the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:06.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Two enemies, the GSS and the Sheep, \Nhave formed an alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:11.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We have to shut them down before \Nthey become completely coordinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:14.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But, hey, we'll be done by noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:16.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We're killing them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Including the Sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no change to our policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:27.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That said, if someone, a peer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:32.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who has information \Non the enemy... can advise us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:34.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind changing our policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:38.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,A peer's advice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:41.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,For example, a peer in the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:44.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I could trust the advice of one of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:46.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:52.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Although, anyone who lost to me in a game
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:58.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,is bound to get worked to the \Nbone in this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:01.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shred you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:03.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I like that expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a wild beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Got that, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:16.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,As we discussed earlier, \Nno hurting the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,He'd calculated that this would happen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since he made that \Nphone call at the arcade...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,He did it to sow doubt \Nabout me in my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,That son of a bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm game, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, in the Port Mafia,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:59.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,whoever recruits a new member \Nis responsible for their care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:03.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,As a symbol of that, they hand \Ndown one of their belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:06.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,I gave Dazai-kun my coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:08.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,And that's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,It's an old hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:13.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,It belonged to Randou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:23.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he'd been investigating Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:28.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the military facility \Nhe infiltrated was researching
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:32.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,the creation of an artificial gifted by \Ncombining gifted and normal beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Artificial gifted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:38.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the documents he collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:47.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,but only executives have \Npermission to view those files.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think I won't \Npummel you and take it for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't such a fool of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:19:02.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I can answer another question \Nthat you would want answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:10.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,So you see right through me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:14.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me one thing: What exactly \Nis the leader of an organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:19.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,A leader is both the head of the organization\Nand the organization's slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,For the survival and profit \Nof the organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:26.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,they gladly put themselves \Nthrough any manner of filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:30.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,They develop their subordinates \Nand place them where they best fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:35.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,And, if necessary,\N they use and dispose of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:40.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the organization,\N they take on any act of barbarism with glee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,That is a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:50.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,All for the organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:55.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,and for the protection of this beloved city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:19:59.07,Stray Dogs - Italics,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:01.72,Stray Dogs - Italics,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,That's what was missing in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:17.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Then I dedicate my blood \Nand all that I am to you, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:21.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect this organization \Nthat you work to support,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:24.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,and I will work for you \Nto decimate its enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:29.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Our enemies will know the vicious gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,that will crush those \Nwho oppose the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:42.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Port Mafia, \NNakahara Chuuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:53.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking me to \Nthe meeting, old sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that old yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0000,0000,0000,,For your information, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:06.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0000,0000,0000,,The meeting today is with one of \Nthe Mafia's front organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:10.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0000,0000,0000,,Every cup of tea, \Nevery pause in the conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:12.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0000,0000,0000,,affects the Mafia's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:17.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0000,0000,0000,,What if I take part in the \Nmeeting and make them angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,We'll deal with that when it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:23.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,If the boat is so easily tipped,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,it would be more triumphant \Nto destroy it spectacularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:29.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Q,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kyusaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:30.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Q,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Q,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine, when you're older.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Chuuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:42.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think we recruited you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're my dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell you my leg is itchy, \Nyou scratch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:50.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell you I want to eat soba, you threaten\N a soba shop owner into coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:51.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:54.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,So what the hell are you doing \Nin Kouyou-san's direct command?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Working your way up the ladder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:57.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Smooth sailing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're young! Go do some grunt work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:02.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you scheming bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:05.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I joined the Port Mafia of my own accord!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Chuuya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to be your \Nhenchman or your dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:12.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really such a good idea to have \Nthese two in the same organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:14.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Kouyou,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:18.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Only a diamond can polish a diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:25.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-sensei, those words you \Ntold me and Fukuzawa-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:29.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find out if you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:37.25,sign_32391_313_Seven_Years_Late,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Seven Years Later\N (Present Day)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:37.25,sign_32391_314_Somewhere___Toky,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere, \NTokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:43.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the events \Nsurrounding the recruitment of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:47.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0000,0000,0000,,Port Mafia executives \NNakahara Chuuya and Dazai Osamu.
